Text: Sorry peeps, 12/2 STOSSEL will be delayed until 12/4 or 12/5 due to a cable signal dropout resulting in a receiver lockup. Foobar.

Okay...well it turned out that STOSSEL for 12/2 was a replay of the show of 20101007 on the national debt. So, I fussed over nothing. That was a good show, though, so please give it a tumble if you've not yet seen it!
